title: I Did The Crossword With City Bankers | StreetSmart
description: In this video, Max Fosh takes to the streets to do a crossword puzzle with city bankers.
summary: Max Fosh interacts with city bankers while doing a crossword puzzle.
payoff: The humor comes from the contrast between the serious and professional demeanor of the bankers and the lighthearted crossword puzzle activity, showcasing the unexpected fun side of these individuals.
